639
00:31:23,840 --> 00:31:25,465
Xin lỗi.

640
00:31:32,473 --> 00:31:35,225
Cô ấy tuyệt chứ?

641
00:31:35,226 --> 00:31:37,561
Những Kẻ Xấu.

642
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:41,273
